			<div id="DickQuotes">
				<div id="quote">"(M)ost analysts...pick out what they suspect intuitively is the most likely answer, then look at the available information from the point of view of whether or not it supports this answer. If the evidence seems to support the favorite hypothesis, analysts pat themselves on the back and look no further.
"</div>
				<div id="dick"> -- Richards Heuer, ACH Creator</div>
